# Local issue-investigation scratch directories (screenshots, copied
# prefs, notes); named after the issue number. gitignore globs can't
# express "one or more digits", so cover 1-6 digit names explicitly.
# Leading / anchors to the repo root; trailing / matches directories only.
/[0-9]/
/[0-9][0-9]/
/[0-9][0-9][0-9]/
/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]/
/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]/
/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]/

# Live AI harness config (API keys) written by tools/run_ai_live.sh; never commit.
.iterm2-ai-live.json
